---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<style>
  .about-me-text {
    color: #f8f8f2; /* Foreground */
  }

  .about-me-list {
    color: #6272a4; /* Comment (a softer alternative to match the theme) */
  }

  .about-me-title {
    color: #bd93f9; /* Purple */
  }
</style>

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me" class="about-me-title">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 about-me-text">
    <div class="text-sm font-light">
      <p>
        Hello! My name is Jordan, and I'm currently a full-time Software Developer at Full Sail.
        <br />
        My skillset includes:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside about-me-list">
        <li>Java</li>
        <li>Lua</li>
        <li>C++</li>
        <li>Astro (Learning)</li>
        <li>GDScript (Learning)</li>
        <li>Unreal Visual Scripting (Learning)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        Beyond coding, I have a passion for design, 3D modeling, and cars. I also enjoy collecting old flagship phones, as they represent a bygone era that fascinates me.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        I'm always eager to expand my skillset and find the right solution for every project I work on.
      </p>
  </div>
</Card>

